# Project Atlas — migration 0005: audit_event with mandatory actor (Apr 7)

@D atlas_finance|Audit event table — actor now mandatory (closes legacy gap)

@T AuditEvent|Append-only audit events mirrored from Kafka — actor required at row level
audit_id|UUID|N|PK|Primary key
event_ts|TIMESTAMPTZ|N||Event timestamp
actor|VARCHAR(120)|N||Acting principal (mandatory in new platform)
entity|VARCHAR(40)|N||Entity affected
entity_id|UUID|N||Entity identifier
operation|VARCHAR(20)|N||Operation type
prior_version|INTEGER|Y||Previous version, for SUPERSEDE
new_version|INTEGER|Y||Resulting version
@E AuditEvent.operation|INSERT,UPDATE,SUPERSEDE,REVERSE,CLOSE,GATE
